<plot>Nikki, a young and successful New Yorker, is falling in love with her German boyfriend, Toby. Her protected world is shaken when she meets Isaac, a holocaust survivor and co-worker. She begins to have misconceptions about Toby, as she sees something that is not there. Nikki's doubts bring her into an emotional turmoil of fear and prejudice.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?079894</url></doc>
